### About
We specialize in advanced numerical and scientific computing and provide consultancy and software development services. Our domain experts span machine learning, computer vision, brain imaging, signal processing, realtime and web applications. Our mission is to aggregate focused teams to solve your scientific problem.

### Clients
Our clients presently include academic institutions, non-profits and other organizations.
